sql:
SELECT p.product_name, s.shipment_date
FROM Products p
JOIN Order_Items oi ON p.product_id = oi.product_id
JOIN Shipment_Items si ON oi.order_item_id = si.order_item_id
JOIN Shipments s ON si.shipment_id = s.shipment_id;
question: List the names of the products being shipped and the corresponding shipment date.
